00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:42,300
(Taxi)
a wonderful deal.

26
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,240
Heading to Pudong.

27
00:01:43,350 --> 00:01:44,230
Congratulations.

28
00:01:44,230 --> 00:01:45,400
- You...
- Li,

29
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,400
here's the thing.

30
00:01:46,540 --> 00:01:48,840
Could you give me more shifts
during the Chinese New Year?

31
00:01:49,230 --> 00:01:50,710
Well, I'll visit relatives

32
00:01:50,710 --> 00:01:51,680
during the day.

33
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,480
Can you arrange more night shifts?

34
00:01:54,790 --> 00:01:56,920
Qian Kang, aren't you from Jiangxi?

35
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,240
Well,

36
00:01:58,250 --> 00:01:59,330
aren't you going home?

37
00:02:00,350 --> 00:02:01,430
Well, Qian Kang is

38
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:02,270
a live-in son-in-law.

39
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,120
He won't go back.

40
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,040
Didn't you know that?

41
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:05,430
What do you mean?

42
00:02:05,710 --> 00:02:06,790
Tell me the details.

43
00:02:08,140 --> 00:02:09,030
Tell me more about it.

44
00:02:09,870 --> 00:02:10,710
Thanks, Li.

45
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,560
Start from the 2nd day
of Chinese New Year.

46
00:02:22,190 --> 00:02:23,680
You must be careful.

47
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,080
Mao Tou!

48
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,560
Hold it tight!

49
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,840
- What?
- It's just a computer.

50
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,630
I can make a couple of rounds.

51
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:36,840
Why did you call him over?

52
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,960
You don't understand.

53
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:39,590
He's a technical consultant.

54
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:40,870
It's different, okay?

55
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:42,520
This way?

56
00:02:42,870 --> 00:02:44,560
Yes, this door here.

57
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,750
Technical consultant.

58
00:02:49,710 --> 00:02:51,080
Mao Tou, be careful.

59
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:52,990
The monitor needs to be upright.

60
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,840
Mao Tou.

61
00:02:55,130 --> 00:02:56,430
Set the monitor upright.

62
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,240
Be careful.

63
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,080
Oh, close the curtains.

64
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:06,240
Mao Tou, close the curtains.

65
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:15,870
Then...

66
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,120
What's this?

67
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:21,960
It's a mess.

68
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,750
Now put this

69
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,590
on top of it.

70
00:03:29,140 --> 00:03:30,000
It worked!

71
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,150
It's really moving!

72
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:32,920
Thank you, Chang Wuji.

73
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:34,840
It's okay. You're welcome.

74
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:39,190
Brother Xiao Han has loved watching

75
00:03:39,470 --> 00:03:40,630
the stars since childhood.

76
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,840
Now, he's the president
of the Astronomy Club.

77
00:03:45,210 --> 00:03:46,050
Mao Tou,

78
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,080
do you think

79
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:48,910
Brother Xiao Han will like this gift?

80
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:55,150
He definitely will.

81
00:03:58,750 --> 00:03:59,590
Be gentle.

82
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,360
Hello.

83
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:07,310
Hello.

84
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,430
- Qian Lin?
- Brother, is that you?

85
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:12,910
Well, hang up first.

86
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:15,520
I... I'll call you in a minute.

87
00:04:20,310 --> 00:04:21,750
I'll go into the room.

88
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,000
Qian Lin.

89
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,120
We can talk now.

90
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,270
Brother,

91
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,920
are you really not coming back?

92
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,070
You have no idea.

93
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:50,430
Mom cried again about it this morning.

94
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,720
Tell her not to cry, okay?

95
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,480
You know

96
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,510
the situation here, right?

97
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:57,720
My mother-in-law isn't well.

98
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:58,670
How about this?

99
00:04:58,740 --> 00:04:59,600
I'll bring Jiayue

100
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,190
to visit you in summer, alright?

101
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:02,670
By the way,

102
00:05:02,950 --> 00:05:04,360
did you receive the money and gifts?

103
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,160
Have a good Chinese New Year.

104
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,230
As

105
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:10,270
your younger brother,

106
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:12,240
it's not my place to say this.

107
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,080
However,

108
00:05:13,140 --> 00:05:14,390
you've really spoiled your wife.

109
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,640
Honestly,

110
00:05:15,650 --> 00:05:17,720
you have no idea
what the villagers said.

111
00:05:17,890 --> 00:05:20,160
They said you went to Shanghai
to be a live-in son-in-law.

112
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,040
You drink her footbath water every day,

113
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,740
and your daughter doesn't have
our surname.

114
00:05:23,740 --> 00:05:24,630
They said our family

115
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:26,430
sold sons to make a living.

116
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:28,920
What nonsense is this?

117
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:31,630
These gossipers always spread rumors

118
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:32,720
in the village,

119
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:33,740
you can't stop them.

120
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,160
Just let them talk.

121
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,510
Tell Mom to ignore them.

122
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,800
Hello, Qian Lin,

123
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,010
I'm Xiu'e.

124
00:05:40,010 --> 00:05:41,240
Oh, Xiu'e.

125
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,160
Hello, hello.

126
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:44,720
- Tell Dad and Mom
- Hello.

127
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,750
our whole family is going back

128
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,160
to Jiangxi this time.

129
00:05:48,590 --> 00:05:49,720
- It's a deal, okay?
- Okay.

130
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,560
I'm hanging up.

131
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:01,880
Xiu'e...

132
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,000
What are you doing?

133
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:04,990
Stop!

134
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:07,160
I'm back.

135
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,800
What are you doing?

136
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,830
Your mom is the best wife ever.

137
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:20,670
Jiayue.

138
00:06:21,180 --> 00:06:22,040
I'll tell her, okay?

139
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:24,230
This year,

140
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:25,830
we're going back to Jiangxi.

141
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:29,720
Thank you.

142
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,040
See you on the 6th day.

143
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:48,390
I hope Mom can book the return tickets
on the 5th day.

144
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,390
If I can't make it back by the 6th day,

145
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,720
I'll cry my eyes out.

146
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,190
It's okay.

147
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:05,870
If you can't make it back,

148
00:07:05,870 --> 00:07:06,890
just don't come back.

149
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,390
It's not a big deal.

150
00:07:08,510 --> 00:07:09,360
Mao Tou!

151
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,400
Sister Jiayue.

152
00:07:15,030 --> 00:07:16,310
Will you call me

153
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,870
after going back to Jiangxi?

154
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,440
Of course.

155
00:07:20,450 --> 00:07:21,680
What's my home number?

156
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,860
During the Chinese New Year,

157
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,480
you'll visit Brother Xiao Han anyway.

158
00:07:30,950 --> 00:07:32,480
I'll call Brother Xiao Han,

159
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,950
and you can answer it.

160
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,000
It's different.

161
00:07:37,950 --> 00:07:39,000
Brother Xiao Han

162
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,840
is not me.

163
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:42,310
I can't follow him around every day.

164
00:07:42,830 --> 00:07:43,670
Aren't you already?

165
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:56,920
Here's my number.

166
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,390
Please remember it.

167
00:08:02,830 --> 00:08:03,720
Call me, okay?

168
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,480
If you can't make it back,

169
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:08,560
I'll show

170
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,510
Brother Xiao Han

171
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:10,750
the gift you prepared.

172
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,600
After all, it's from your heart.

173
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:28,920
Dad, why did you come in?

174
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,000
What are you doing?

175
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,550
Why are you up this late?

176
00:08:32,550 --> 00:08:33,390
What are you doing?

177
00:08:34,510 --> 00:08:36,390
What are you here at this hour?

178
00:08:36,910 --> 00:08:38,150
Listen carefully, don't think

179
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:39,930
you can slack off

180
00:08:39,930 --> 00:08:41,200
just because it's vacation.

181
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,440
If you

182
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,720
score last in the final exams

183
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,150
in the next semester,

184
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,160
I'll...

185
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,440
Got it.

186
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,000
It's late. Can you stop scolding me?

187
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:52,910
Well,

188
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,080
on the 3rd day,

189
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:55,550
we'll visit Uncle Wang.

190
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:58,360
On the 4th day, we'll visit my aunt.

191
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,240
How about the 6th Day?

192
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:00,550
On the 6th day...

193
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,750
No plans yet.

194
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:03,720
Good then.

195
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,560
What's wrong?

196
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:05,960
Nothing.

197
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,440
Go to sleep.

198
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,870
Jiayue, do you remember this place?

199
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:39,710
Sister-in-law!

200
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:41,110
Brother!

201
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,510
Brother, you're back!

202
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,840
Where are Mom and Dad?

203
00:09:44,030 --> 00:09:44,870
Inside the house.

204
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,080
Qian Lin!

205
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,510
Brother is back!

206
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:49,960
Let me help you.

207
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,120
Help Xiu'e.

208
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:52,630
- Let me help you.
- No need!

209
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:54,670
- Give it to me.
- Dad, Mom!

210
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,670
- This is your uncle.
- Hello, Uncle.

211
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,640
Jiayue has grown so tall.

212
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,440
Brother!

213
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,800
Qian Yu!

214
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:06,630
You've grown so tall!

215
00:10:07,030 --> 00:10:08,360
Last time, you were a little kid.

216
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,560
Dad!

217
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,080
Mom!

218
00:10:11,390 --> 00:10:12,230
Dad!

219
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,600
We're back to visit you.

220
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:15,510
Grandpa and Grandma.

221
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,750
Hello, Grandpa, Grandma.

222
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:18,440
Dad, Mom.

223
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:20,350
Xiu'e.

224
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,420
Why are you standing there?

225
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:22,720
Give the gifts to my parents

226
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:24,030
and brothers.

227
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:25,750
Mom, Dad,

228
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:28,480
we've prepared
health supplements for you.

229
00:10:28,790 --> 00:10:29,630
Thank you.

230
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:30,480
Brother.

231
00:10:30,930 --> 00:10:32,010
- This is for you.
- Xiu'e!

232
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,080
A wool blanket.

233
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,240
- Xiu'e!
- Thank you, Xiu'e!

234
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,080
And Weihao's gift.

235
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,480
Where's Hao? Where's my nephew?

236
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,360
Hao.

237
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:39,270
- Hao, come here.
- Hao, good boy.

238
00:10:39,370 --> 00:10:40,240
Say hello.

239
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,080
Hao, come on.

240
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,120
Say hello.

241
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:44,120
Uncle, Aunt.

242
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,080
Hao.

243
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,240
Here's your gift.

244
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:48,440
Electronic Dictionary.

245
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,840
Awesome!
Does it have video games?

246
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,800
Sure.

247
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:53,750
Weiye, Here.

248
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,630
- You're too kind.
- Want Want Gift Pack.

249
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,440
Thank you.

250
00:10:57,450 --> 00:10:58,600
So many snacks.

251
00:10:58,750 --> 00:10:59,590
Where's Jiali?

252
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,600
She's in the kitchen.

253
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:03,630
Does she have a gift?

254
00:11:04,030 --> 00:11:06,200
Jiayue, go to the kitchen
to play with your cousin.

255
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,160
Okay.

256
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:09,030
- She's inside.
- In the kitchen.

257
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,240
This is so great.

258
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:14,090
Jiali,

259
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:18,200
here's the new backpack
my parents got for you.

260
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,680
Thank you.

261
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,240
Why are you cooking alone here?

262
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,910
You're our guests from the city.

263
00:11:34,390 --> 00:11:35,790
A countryside girl like me

264
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:39,080
can only cook for you.

265
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:44,590
Come on.

266
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,150
Dad, let's have a drink.

267
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:47,510
Have a drink.

268
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:49,320
- Brother.
- Qian Yu, Qian Lin, thanks.

269
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,390
Need anything else?

270
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:51,910
Sister-in-law, make it spicier.

271
00:11:52,270 --> 00:11:53,150
You haven't changed.

272
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:54,160
Can't find it in Shanghai.

273
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,280
Come on.

274
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,440
Sit down and eat.

275
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,350
Jiayue,

276
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,870
I heard you got into a key high school.

277
00:12:03,890 --> 00:12:05,040
Your mom said

278
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,670
now that you're
in this high school,

279
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,320
you're already halfway

280
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:10,000
to a prestigious university.

281
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,630
Their College Entrance Exam.

282
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:15,030
Huh.

283
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:19,360
Why are you saying?

284
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:21,240
What's wrong with it?

285
00:12:21,770 --> 00:12:23,890
How many local spots
for top universities do you have?

286
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:26,080
How many seats are left
for other provinces?

287
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:28,960
Aren't you aware of

288
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,440
your own level?

