297
00:12:44,390 --> 00:12:45,230
Jiali.

298
00:12:45,730 --> 00:12:46,910
Are you out of your mind?

299
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,550
Just eat your meal.

300
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,270
You're a girl.

301
00:12:50,390 --> 00:12:51,360
