A random question from our workbook.

307
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:04,800
Jiali.

308
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:06,080
What are you doing?

309
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:17,270
We don't get tested on this.

310
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,380
You don't get tested on

311
00:13:19,390 --> 00:13:20,600
