322
00:13:38,550 --> 00:13:39,440
Do you understand?

323
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:41,560
No mindless memorization
and endless practice.

324
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:43,360
We test a person's ability.

325
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:45,550
Sounds nice in theory.

326
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:49,080
Fine, I'll also ask you a question.

327
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:51,600
