339
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:15,600
This is well-rounded education.

340
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,660
We test comprehensive ability.

341
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:20,920
Then you...

342
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:24,080
Jiayue.

343
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:25,630
That was impressive.

344
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,630
Don't argue with her.

345
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:29,600
Jiali, Jiayue is our guest.

346
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:31,240
Watch your mouth, okay?

347
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,440
Eat dinner.

348
00:14:35,390 --> 00:14:36,230
Xiu'e.

349
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,240
Come on, try this.

350
00:14:37,250 --> 00:14:38,440
I'm full. I'm full.

351
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:39,360
Thank you.

352
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:40,200
Jiayue.

353
00:14:43,940 --> 00:14:46,580
(Yingmo Community)

354
00:14:53,630 --> 00:14:54,630
Mao Tou.

355
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:55,750
Are you there?

356
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:57,920
Coming.

357
00:15:00,750 --> 00:15:01,910
God Grandma, why are you here?

358
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,750
Mao Tou, what are you doing?

359
00:15:04,910 --> 00:15:05,750
I...

360
00:15:07,030 --> 00:15:08,270
I'm fixing the computer.

361
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:11,080
The mailman delivered a letter.

362
00:15:11,220 --> 00:15:12,360
- I brought it here.
- Okay.

363
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,200
It's for your dad.

364
00:15:14,310 --> 00:15:15,210
From Japan.

365
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,160
Don't forget to give it to him.

366
00:15:25,900 --> 00:15:28,900
(Yang Min)

367
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,080
Pack things up.

368
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,040
Why?

369
00:15:42,510 --> 00:15:43,350
Your mom...

370
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,400
Yang Min

371
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:45,510
