372
00:16:16,040 --> 00:16:17,000
Yang Min wrote a letter.

373
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:17,970
(Yang Min)

374
00:16:17,970 --> 00:16:18,990
I wanted to get a divorce,

375
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:19,960
and she agreed.

376
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,320
She'll be in Shanghai soon.

377
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,360
Aiping, don't worry.

378
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:23,670
I'll end this marriage

379
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:25,150
quickly and completely.

380
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:26,550
I'll be free again.

381
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:27,590
Then we can

382
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:28,680
grow old together.

383
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:33,120
I thought they divorced long ago.

384
00:16:34,150 --> 00:16:36,240
Dad said she betrayed us.

385
00:16:36,550 --> 00:16:37,600
He wanted to trap her.

386
00:16:38,150 --> 00:16:39,910
If she dares to get married in Japan,

387
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:41,120
she'll commit bigamy.

388
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:43,870
Divorce.

389
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,910
Back then, she was entangled

390
00:16:46,910 --> 00:16:48,550
with an old man in Japan.

391
00:16:49,440 --> 00:16:50,550
I was so pissed off.

392
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:51,790
She wanted a divorce. No way.

393
00:16:51,790 --> 00:16:52,790
How could I divorce her?

394
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,720
Now I want to divorce her.

395
00:16:54,910 --> 00:16:55,960
I'll negotiate with her,

396
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:57,550
and I need a strategy.

397
00:16:57,550 --> 00:16:58,510
I've figured it out.

398
00:16:58,510 --> 00:17:00,200
This time, Mao Tou and I

399
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,360
will put on a show for her.

400
00:17:04,350 --> 00:17:05,190
A show?

401
00:17:05,550 --> 00:17:06,400
What kind of show?

402
00:17:07,030 --> 00:17:07,870
Take a guess.

403
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:10,830
We'll pack up,

404
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,000
and move back

405
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:13,240
to the old house.

406
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:15,240
Why?

407
00:17:15,550 --> 00:17:17,070
You know Yang Min, right?

408
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:18,400
She's ruthless.

409
00:17:18,830 --> 00:17:20,200
We're not divorced yet,

410
00:17:20,510 --> 00:17:22,000
if she knew I've made a fortune.

411
00:17:22,310 --> 00:17:23,240
She'll make a scene

412
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:24,270
and share my properties.

413
00:17:25,830 --> 00:17:27,110
All the money I've earned

414
00:17:27,110 --> 00:17:28,160
has nothing to do with her.

415
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:29,030
Why should I share it?

416
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:31,830
I'll pretend to be poor

417
00:17:31,830 --> 00:17:32,670
and sick.

418
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:34,310
I told her,

419
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:36,070
"I didn't want to divorce you.

420
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:37,540
Now that I'm unemployed

421
00:17:37,750 --> 00:17:39,240
and sick, I can divorce you.

422
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:40,400
You only need

423
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:41,400
to give me some money."

424
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,110
She agreed in the letter.

425
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,560
Qiming.

426
00:17:44,780 --> 00:17:46,340
It's not right to deceive her like this.

427
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:48,750
I think you two should

428
00:17:48,750 --> 00:17:50,070
have an honest talk

429
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:51,550
and end it peacefully.

430
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:54,160
If she's really struggling,

431
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:55,670
why can't you give her some money?

432
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,030
After all,

433
00:17:57,030 --> 00:17:58,240
she's Mao Tou's mother.

434
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:17,920
Yes! I said, "You're useless!"

435
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:18,760
I'm useless?

436
00:18:18,780 --> 00:18:20,830
I said, "You're useless, loser!"

437
00:18:20,830 --> 00:18:22,510
What about you?
You wander around every day!

438
00:18:22,510 --> 00:18:24,160
Who wanders around? It's you!

439
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,400
You're always gambling!

440
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:26,310
How dare you judge me?

441
00:18:26,310 --> 00:18:27,400
I like it, so what?

442
00:18:27,540 --> 00:18:28,440
None of your business!

443
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:29,590
Then stay out of my business!

444
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:30,880
Why do you care? Shut up!

445
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,110
Who cares? Aren't you ashamed?

446
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:33,750
- Aren't you a mother?
- What's wrong?

447
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:35,070
I'm way better than you, okay?

448
00:18:35,310 --> 00:18:37,200
Who else do you dare to yell at
except for me?

449
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:38,310
Little imp, stop crying!

450
00:18:38,310 --> 00:18:40,000
Zhang Qiming, don't yell at my son!

451
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:41,510
You don't deserve to be his mom!

452
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:10,000
I can even raise a digital pet.

453
00:19:10,270 --> 00:19:11,920
What digital pet?

454
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,270
Stop bragging.

455
00:19:27,270 --> 00:19:28,240
How can you raise a pet?

456
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:29,160
Come tomorrow

457
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:30,480
