460
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:19,160
Dad and Mom have been
in Jiangxi for many years

461
00:20:19,290 --> 00:20:20,560
and still have a northern accent.

462
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:21,830
We're from Hebei.

463
00:20:22,300 --> 00:20:23,550
