464
00:20:23,550 --> 00:20:25,160
Come on, cheers.

465
00:20:25,220 --> 00:20:26,240
Hard to change. Well said.

466
00:20:27,110 --> 00:20:27,950
Qian Kang.

467
00:20:28,550 --> 00:20:29,390
Don't drink too much.

468
00:20:30,070 --> 00:20:30,920
Xiu'e.

469
00:20:31,550 --> 00:20:33,160
It's rare for us

470
00:20:33,550 --> 00:20:34,750
to have fun with our brother.

471
00:20:35,110 --> 00:20:35,960
Don't worry about it.

472
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:36,810
Xiu'e, don't worry.

473
00:20:36,810 --> 00:20:38,030
Women shouldn't

474
00:20:38,030 --> 00:20:39,350
