475
00:20:39,350 --> 00:20:40,760
- Come on.
- Brother.

476
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:41,880
Have some peanuts.

477
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:43,840
Xiu'e.

478
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:45,840
