481
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:52,240
Go.

482
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:53,560
Come on.

483
00:20:54,110 --> 00:20:55,110
Come on.

484
00:20:55,390 --> 00:20:56,240
Alright.

485
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:58,240
Dad, I'll get some peanuts.

486
00:20:58,440 --> 00:20:59,280
Hurry up.

487
00:20:59,590 --> 00:21:00,760
Take the initiative next time.

488
00:21:01,310 --> 00:21:02,750
- Come on, cheers.
- Cheers.

489
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:06,150
Brother,

490
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:08,110
