507
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:38,110
Don't be upset, okay?

508
00:21:38,310 --> 00:21:39,350
We had a deal.

509
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:42,750
Women shouldn't
meddle in men's business.

510
00:21:43,030 --> 00:21:44,160
Well said.

511
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:46,110
I had to convince them.

512
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:47,560
Where's Jiali?

513
00:21:47,750 --> 00:21:48,680
