- Thanks, Xiu'e.

526
00:22:11,830 --> 00:22:12,840
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

527
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:14,480
Come on.

528
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:16,480
Brother,

529
00:22:17,110 --> 00:22:18,790
