541
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:39,160
How dare she disobey?

542
00:22:40,720 --> 00:22:42,110
Money doesn't matter.

543
00:22:42,350 --> 00:22:43,640
Harmony brings happiness.

544
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,830
Come on.

545
00:22:44,830 --> 00:22:45,670
Have another drink.

546
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:47,880
Brother, I'm impressed.

547
00:22:48,090 --> 00:22:49,380
